Overview of Changes in libpeas 1.15.0
====================================

* Add g_autoptr() autocleanup support
* Fix Python tests on OpenBSD
* Fix libpeas crash on windows
* Simplify __all__ support in the Python plugin loader
* Misc bugfixes

* Translation updates:
